{"tid":522919,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬斐森：中聯辦成日搵我","createTime":"2018-01-08T04:10:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-08T07:15:25.000Z","uid":39464,"like":146,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"54ca9d71d5c2d749e9c6cfa9ed87a12990b6bcc4","tid":522919,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T04:10:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180108/large/1515383845_82d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180108%2Flarge%2F1515383845_82d5.jpg&h=c14f9115&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n剛離任的前港大校長馬斐森接受《南華早報》訪問，再講述他任內4年經歷，指經常感受到來自各方壓力，透露中聯辦經常向他提出意見，而在合約即將結束前仍未獲港大校委會主席李國章傾談續約，故在愛丁堡大學向他招手時決定跳槽。<br />\n<br />\n馬斐森在訪問中指希望高等教育不「那麼政治」，但經常感受到來自各方，包括本地官員的壓力，又指中聯辦經常向他給予意見。他又透露本港所有大學領導層都與中聯辦有聯絡，指中聯辦對本地教育有興趣。<br />\n<br />\n對港大將來，他希望港大能繼續國際化，而非只著重與內地合作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180108/57679950\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180108%2F57679950&d=n2QiVH5lzydu35rodligO1zEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=ae67fe39\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180108%2F57679950&h=c27db28b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180108/57679950</a>"},{"pid":"83c752371f426ea63c05ff035bb7533d984ddb3c","tid":522919,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T04:11:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff032d8e4a1d9c0de3d6f4f0a78152b92f30de7","tid":522919,"uid":3241,"like":35,"dislike":5,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T04:13:25.000Z","msg":"搵你講咩先重點，鬼唔知中聯辦干涉香港教育咩"},{"pid":"acdef201e2861d9db3eb63fdd5c2f00fdc42eb52","tid":522919,"uid":93266,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-